reviewText: My three kids, ages 3&4 love Super Samurai Power Rangers, of all the different power rangers this is their favorite.
Yet another collection of episodes in this series. Designed for fans of the show.
if your wanting something watch with the kids this you can not go wrong with the power rangers .This dvd is good and won't have to worry about bad words or blood it safe and clean

I did not use this but for 30 minutes. Laundry room got way to steamy,
just like you were in a sauna. Filled the bottom half way full of water
and started dryer. Floor was all wet from the doors being shut.. Not
good for me in a residential home.
I purchased this DVD for my grandson birthday,he is a big fan of all the Power Rangers DVD works great.

Since the power rangers are not on free TV any more I miss watching it.
I am excited that it is in DVD.

Purchased for grandson who watch all the power ranger on Netflix's
Now they can watch even in their own room.
